name: Michael Vanhook
text: Don't mess with the pencil or water. Otherwise it's a really remarkable setup.

name: Gary Moore
text: First of all, in the spirit of full disclosure, I'm a charter member and current president of the club, so yes, I may be just a bit biased. We welcome visitors to come by. We'll show you our HO scale layout and demonstrate our passion for what some have called "the world's greatest hobby".

name: Brett Scott
text: Great model railroad club.  The layout is unbelievable.  Kid friendly.
